# Experiment 2

## Question 1

List all distinct jobs.

### Query

```sql
SELECT DISTINCT JOB FROM Employee;
```

### Output

Unique job roles displayed.

## Question 2

List all employees in department 30.

### Query

```sql
SELECT * FROM Employee WHERE DeptNo = 30;
```

### Output

Employees from department 30 displayed.

## Question 3

Find department numbers greater than 20.

### Query

```sql
SELECT DeptNo, Dname FROM Department WHERE DeptNo > 20;
```

### Output

Departments with DeptNo > 20 displayed.

