# Experiment 4

## Question 1

Display employees joined before 30-June-80 or after 31-Dec-81.

### Query

```sql
SELECT * FROM Employee WHERE HIREDATE < '30-JUN-80' OR HIREDATE > '31-DEC-81';
```

### Output

Filtered employee records displayed.

## Question 2

Display employees whose name has second letter A.

### Query

```sql
SELECT ENAME FROM Employee WHERE ENAME LIKE '_A%';
```

### Output

Matching names displayed.

