# Experiment 6

## Question 1

Display employee details with department name using DECODE.

### Query

```sql
SELECT EMPNO, ENAME,
DECODE(DEPTNO,10,'RESEARCH',20,'ACCOUNTING',30,'SALES',40,'OPERATIONS') AS DEPT_NAME
FROM Employee;
```

### Output

Employee details with department names displayed.

## Question 2

Display current date.

### Query

```sql
SELECT SYSDATE FROM DUAL;
```

### Output

Current date displayed.

