# Experiment 7

## Question 1

Find highest and lowest salary difference.

### Query

```sql
SELECT MAX(SAL) - MIN(SAL) FROM Employee;
```

### Output

Difference between highest and lowest salary displayed.

## Question 2

Display employees whose commission is greater than 25% of salary.

### Query

```sql
SELECT * FROM Employee WHERE COMM > 0.25 * SAL;
```

### Output

Filtered employee records displayed.

## Question 3

Count employees in each department.

### Query

```sql
SELECT DeptNo, COUNT(*) FROM Employee GROUP BY DeptNo;
```

### Output

Number of employees per department displayed.

